> To enable early media speech recognition, you must manually set this parameter to **true**.', example='fasle'),
  enableITN?: boolean(name='EnableITN', description='Whether to execute ITN during post-processing.  

> When set to **true**, Chinese numerals are converted to Arabic numerals in the output. The default value is **false**.', example='true'),
